  "title": "Class 3 Driver (BDVL Required)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Drive company vehicle for tourist transportation</p></li><li><p>Pick up and drop off passengers from hotels and attractions</p></li><li><p>Follow assigned routes and schedules strictly</p></li><li><p>Ensure passenger safety and comfort at all times</p></li><li><p>Maintain vehicle cleanliness and conduct basic daily checks</p></li><li><p>Comply with traffic rules and company SOPs</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Valid <strong>Singapore Class 3 Driving Licence</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>BDVL (Bus Driver Vocational Licence) – Mandatory</strong></p></li><li><p>Minimum 1 year driving experience in Singapore preferred</p></li><li><p>Good knowledge of Singapore roads</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and responsible</p></li><li><p>Able to work 6 days a week</p></li><li><p>Good attitude and customer service mindset</p></li></ul>",
